Funded Loans

04/09/2021

perdata <- runQuery("select
                        dls.as_of_date,
                        dls.days_past_due,
                        dls.loan_status,
                        dls.loan_contract_id,
                        dls.charged_off_amount,
                        dls.charged_off_principal,
                        dls.seasoning_in_months
                   from monolith.daily_loan_snapshots dls
                   where dls.loan_status not in ('matured','current','in_grace')")
loans <- runQuery("select 
                        ua.id user_application_id, 
                        ua.upstart_id,
                        ua.upstart_application_id,
                        ua.closed_funding_on,
                        ua.use_of_funds,
                        ua.application_datetime::date as application_date,
                        lc.accepted_at::date as accepted_date,
                        lc.apr,
                        lc.contract_years,
                        lc.default_probability,
                        lc.loan_grade,
                        cp.loan_amount,
                        crs.fico_score,
                        cp.loan_contract_id,
                        crs.vantage_score,
                        e.degree_type,
                        e.institution_type,
                        e.undergraduate_major_id,
                        uacc.user_id,
                        sv.referring_domain,
                        sv.referrer,
                        sv.os,
                        sv.utm_source,
                        sv.browser,
                        add.zip_code,
                        add.state,
                        qs.annual_income,
                        qs.general_dq_reasons,
                        qs.monthly_debt,
                        qs.transunion_dti,
                        qs.equifax_dti,
                        qs.dti,
                        cr.individual_credit_history_days,
                        cr.s0y2_birthdate_ccyymm as birthyear,
                        cr.at01_number_of_trades as number_of_accounts,
                        cr.at33a_total_balance_of_open_trades_verified_in_past_12_months as total_balance,
                        cr.num_inquiries_past_6_months as inquiries_past_6_months,
                        jobs.category as job_type,
                        jobs.from::date as job_started_date,
                        ho.ownership_type as homeownership_type
                  FROM monolith.user_applications ua
                  INNER JOIN monolith.loan_contracts lc
                  ON lc.upstart_application_id=ua.upstart_application_id
                  INNER JOIN monolith.contract_pricings cp
                  ON cp.loan_contract_id=lc.id
                  INNER JOIN monolith.pricing_outputs as po
                  on po.id = ua.selected_pricing_output_id
                  INNER JOIN monolith.pricings as p
                  on p.id = po.pricing_id
                  INNER JOIN monolith.credit_report_summaries as crs
                  on crs.credit_report_id=p.credit_report_id
                  INNER JOIN monolith.educations e
                  on e.upstart_application_id = ua.upstart_application_id
                  INNER JOIN monolith.user_accounts uacc
                  on uacc.id = ua.user_account_id
                  INNER JOIN monolith.approvals app
                  on app.user_application_id=ua.id
                  LEFT JOIN monolith.site_visits sv
                  on sv.user_id = uacc.user_id
                  LEFT JOIN monolith.addresses add
                  on add.id=app.address_id
                  LEFT JOIN monolith.qualification_statuses qs
                  on qs.upstart_application_id=ua.upstart_application_id
                  LEFT JOIN transunion.credit_reports cr
                  on cr.id=crs.credit_report_id
                  LEFT JOIN monolith.jobs
                  on jobs.upstart_application_id=ua.upstart_application_id
                  LEFT JOIN monolith.home_ownerships ho
                  on ho.upstart_application_id = ua.upstart_application_id
                  WHERE ua.decision_status='funded'
                        and crs.owner_type='User'")

loans <- loans[!duplicated(loans$upstart_application_id)]
loans[,delinquent:=ifelse(loan_contract_id %in% unique(perdata[(loan_status %in% c("delinquent","charged_off","partially_charged_off") ) & seasoning_in_months <=36]$loan_contract_id),1,0)]

loans[,chargedoff:=ifelse(loan_contract_id %in% unique(perdata[loan_status %in% c("charged_off","partially_charged_off") & seasoning_in_months <=36]$loan_contract_id),1,0)]




loans[,loan_year:=year(closed_funding_on)]
loans[,birthyear:=as.numeric(substr(birthyear,5,8))]
loans[,borrower_age:=loan_year-birthyear]
loans[,years_at_job:=loan_year-year(job_started_date)]

loans[,utm_source2:=ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(utm_source,"google"),"Google",
                                 ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(utm_source,"facebook"),"Facebook",
                                  ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(utm_source,"upstart") | is.na(utm_source),"Direct",
                                   ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(utm_source,"credit_karma")| stri_detect_fixed(utm_source,"karma"),"Credit Karma",
                                    ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(utm_source,"lendingtree"),"Lending Tree",
                                     ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(utm_source,"thepennyhoarder"),"The Penny Hoarder",
                                      ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(utm_source,"nerdwallet"),"Nerdwallet",
                                       ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(utm_source,"experian"),"Other","Other"))))))))]

loans[,utm_source2:=ifelse(is.na(utm_source),"Direct",utm_source2)]


loans[,os:=tolower(os)]
loans[,os:=ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(os,"windows"),"Windows",
                                 ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(os,"ios"),"IOS",
                                  ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(os,"android") ,"Android",
                                   ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(os,"mac"),"MacOS",
                                    ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(os,"chrome"),"Chrome","Other")))))]

loans[,browser:=tolower(browser)]
loans[,browser:=ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(browser,"safari"),"Safari",
                                 ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(browser,"ie"),"Edge",
                                  ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(browser,"chrome") ,"Chrome",
                                   ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(browser,"edge"),"Edge",
                                    ifelse(stri_detect_fixed(browser,"firefox"),"Firefox","Other")))))]


loans[,vantagebin:=floor(vantage_score/5)*5]
loans[,ficobin:=floor(fico_score/5)*5]
loans[,defaultprobbin:=floor(default_probability*100/5)*5]
loans[,defaultprobbin:=ifelse(defaultprobbin>=50,50,defaultprobbin)]
loans[,vantagecat:=ifelse(vantage_score<=625,"600-625",ifelse(vantage_score<=650,"626-650",ifelse(vantage_score<=700,"651-700","701-850")))]

loans[,state_year:=paste(loan_year,state)]
loans[,zip_year:=paste(zip_code,state)]
loans[,credit_history:=floor(individual_credit_history_days/365)]

loans[,educational_attainment:=ifelse(degree_type %in% c("Associate"),1,ifelse(degree_type %in% c("Bachelor's"),2,ifelse(degree_type %in% c("Masters","MBA","MD","PhD"),3,0)))]


loans[,use_of_funds2 :=ifelse(use_of_funds %in% c("credit_card_refinancing","debt_consolidation"),use_of_funds,"0ther")]

1.3 Panel C

temp <- loans[loan_year>=2019,.(no=.N),by=utm_source2]
temp[,pct:=no*100/sum(no)]

ggplot(temp,aes(x=reorder(utm_source2, -pct),y=pct))+geom_bar(stat="identity",fill="royalblue")+ labs(x="",y="Percent of loans (%)",title = "Panel C: Refferer (in or after 2019)")+theme_minimal()+scale_y_continuous(labels=function(x) format(x, big.mark = ",", scientific = FALSE))

1.4 Panel D

temp <- loans[loan_year>=2019,.(no=.N),by=use_of_funds]
setorder(temp,-no)
temp[,use_of_funds:=ifelse(.I>6,"other",use_of_funds)]
temp <- copy(temp[,.(no=sum(no)),by=use_of_funds])
temp[,pct:=no*100/sum(no)]

ggplot(temp,aes(x=reorder(use_of_funds, -pct),y=pct))+geom_bar(stat="identity",fill="royalblue")+ labs(x="",y="Percent of loans (%)",title = "Panel D: Loan Purpose (in or after 2019)")+theme_minimal()+scale_y_continuous(labels=function(x) format(x, big.mark = ",", scientific = FALSE))+theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90))

2 Figure 3

initialpull <- runQuery("
                  select
                    b.user_account_id,
                    e.pull_date as initial_pull_date
                  FROM monolith.upstart_applications as a
                  LEFT JOIN monolith.user_applications as b
                  on b.upstart_application_id = a.id
                  LEFT JOIN monolith.credit_report_summaries as e
                  on e.user_account_id=b.user_account_id
                  where a.decision_status in ('disqualified') and e.reason in ('initial')
                  ")

initialpull <- initialpull[!duplicated(initialpull)]
setorder(initialpull,user_account_id,initial_pull_date)
initialpull <- initialpull[!is.na(initial_pull_date)]
initialpull <- initialpull[!duplicated(initialpull$user_account_id)]
apps <- runQuery("
                  select
                    a.id as upstart_application_id,
                    a.upstart_id,
                    b.user_account_id,
                    d.bc107s_number_of_30_and_60_days_past_due_ratings_on_credit_card_trades as n_cc_del_3060,
                    d.bc108s_number_of_90_or_more_days_past_due_ratings_on_credit_card_trades as n_cc_del90,
                    e.pull_date,
                    e.vantage_score
                  FROM monolith.upstart_applications as a
                  LEFT JOIN monolith.user_applications as b
                  on b.upstart_application_id = a.id
                  LEFT JOIN monolith.credit_report_summaries as e
                  on e.user_account_id=b.user_account_id
                  LEFT JOIN transunion.credit_reports as d
                  on d.id = e.credit_report_id
                  where a.decision_status in ('disqualified') 
                  ")

apps <- merge(apps,initialpull)

apps[,monthssinceapp:= round(as.numeric(pull_date - initial_pull_date)/(365.25/12))]
apps[,appyear:=year(initial_pull_date)]
apps[,vantagebin:=floor(vantage_score/5)*5]
apps[,ccdel:=n_cc_del_3060+n_cc_del90]
temp <- apps[ monthssinceapp<=13 & ccdel<10] 
temp <- temp[user_account_id %in% unique(temp[monthssinceapp==0]$user_account_id) & user_account_id %in% unique(temp[monthssinceapp %in% 10:13]$user_account_id)]

sample1 <- temp[temp$monthssinceapp==0 & ccdel==0]
temp <- temp[monthssinceapp %in% 10:13]
setorderv(temp,c("user_account_id","ccdel"),c(1,-1))
temp <- temp[!duplicated(temp$user_account_id)]
temp <- temp[,c("user_account_id","ccdel")]
names(temp) <- c("user_account_id","ccdel2")

sample1 <- merge(sample1,temp,by="user_account_id")
sample1[,ccdel:=ifelse(ccdel2>ccdel,1,0)]
reg <- list()

reg[[1]] <- felm(ccdel~factor(vantagebin)|appyear|0|appyear,data=sample1[vantagebin<=760 & vantagebin>=620])

coef_plot_1reg(reg[[1]],"factor(vantagebin)",620)+ ylab(expression(beta[f]))
